Preheat the oven to 150C/130C Fan/Gas 2.In a food processor, pulse together the onion, garlic, herbs, spring onions and rapeseed oil.In a bowl, mix the blended ingredients with the sausagemeat, apricots and parkin. Add the egg and season with salt and pepper.Roll into little balls and place on a lined baking sheet and bake for around 25 minutes.